Package: musicbrainz
Type: Package
Title: Bindings for the 'musicbrainz' Database API
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-11
Authors@R: c(person("Iris", "Lennon", email = "ningxilai@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Dmytro", "Perepolkin", email = "dperepolkin@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
             person("MetaBrainz Foundation", role = "aut", comment = "MetaBrainz"))
Description: Utilising the 'MusicBrainz Database' API (see <https://musicbrainz.org/doc/Development/XML_Web_Service/Version_2>
    for more information), retrieve information about artists, release groups, releases, recordings, works, labels, 
    areas, events, instruments, places, series, annotations, genres and URLs. Supports synchronous and asynchronous 
    operations, includes rate limiting, caching and various output formats.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
